<span id="freeTextContainer17071209317848610352">Nice read... a first book by the author but the writing is pretty matured but easy to read... the flow of the story too is very nice.... narratives with deep meanings used at few places.. it is creditable... at few places author explains complex things using simple examples... the story-line has all the required elements in accurate amount... loved to read the book.. awaiting the next book by the author..</span>

          </span>
